4”** of the Document **”Luật Doanh nghiệp sốAB/CD/QH”** will be assigned the Node ID of ” **AB/CD/QH_chapter_IV_C_3** ”  \\nThe Node attribute extraction follows a sequential and continuous process, where the system processes the text line by line while storing the higher-order structural hierarchy in a stateful dictionary for position retrieval. This approach ensures accurate identification of each node’s ID and its corresponding text at the cost of increased computation due to the sequential nature of processing. However, from the research about different Vietnamese legal document types, we have learnt that each type of document follows a different hierarchical structure, we later narrowed down the scope to a specific set of most relevant document types consisting of Law (following the proposed structure) and Decree/ Resolution/ Circular/ Decision (with no Chapter level) to simplify the extraction process (from which we applied the filter to the original document corpus).', metadata={'header_2': '**Structural Parsing**'}), embedding=[-0.023101806640625, 0.058685302734375, 0.0112457275390625, -0.032806396484375, 0.039642333984375, 0.0168609619140625, -0.0022640228271484375, -0.02520751953125, -0.03692626953125, 0.004253387451171875, 0.01141357421875, -0.00815582275390625, -0.03094482421875, -0.021728515625, 0.014892578125, 0.0188140869140625, 0.023529052734375, -0.0189971923828125, 0.0168609619140625, 0.0264739990234375, 0.05615234375, 0.0033626556396484375, 0.03582763671875, 0.017364501953125, -0.004276275634765625, -0.03265380859375, 0.01235198974609375, 0.01515960693359375, 0.0310821533203125, -0.0087738037109375, -0.00830078125, -0.01123809814453125, 0.038360595703125, -0.0026454925537109375, 0.0009012222290039062, 0.028961181640625, -0.048126220703125, 0.0039825439453125, -0.0230255126953125, 0.01554107666015625, 0.05657958984375, 0.016571044921875, -0.001430511474609375, -0.01418304443359375, -0.00963592529296875, 0.0243377685546875, -0.01739501953125, 0.0192