paktEmbeddingEntry(id='27', chunk=CompaktChunk(header=<MarkdownHeader.H2: '##'>, header_type=<MarkdownHeader.H2: '##'>, header_name='faq crawled dataset', content='To construct a grounded and resource-efficient dataset, we use a crawled FAQ dataset as a grounding and enrichment layer for LLM-generated QA data. Several limitations were identified in the crawled official FAQ data, including the absence of explicit supporting context fields and the lack of transparent document source attribution for each question. These issues substantially reduce the reliability and trustworthiness of direct evaluation based on the FAQ alone; as a result, rather than directly reusing FAQ questions, this dataset guides the generation pipeline through typical and semantic constraints. Vietnamese tax law FAQs reflect how taxpayers naturally phrase questions and how authorities communicate complex legal rules in accessible language, helping bridge the gap between formal legal texts and retrieval tasks.  \\n25  \\nGroup Project  \\nTax Legal Retrieval with Graph Representation Assistant  \\nGroup 55  \\nThe FAQs are collected through a structured **Extract-Transform-Load (ETL)** crawling pipeline that systematically gathers question-answer pairs from authoritative sources such as government websites ( _gdt.gov.vn_ ) and legal libraries ( _thuvienphapluat.vn_ ). The pipeline uses Selenium-based extractors to handle dynamic content, pagination and JavaScript rendered pages. Each extracted record contains not only the question and answer text but also supporting legal references, timestamps, source URLs and provenance metadata. The data is streamed incrementally into checkpointed CSV files to support reproducibility and fault tolerance.  \\n|**Field**|**Value**|\\n|---|---|\\n|source|thuvienphapluat|\\n|question_source|https://thuvienphapluat.vn/hoi-dap-phap-luat/c...|\\n|question|Người nộp thuếcó trách nhiệm gì...|\\n|answer|Căn cứtheo Điều 17 Luật Quản lý thuế2019 sửa...|\\n|created_time|14