eval phase, we employed a standard Similarity Search mechanism that calculates the Cosine Similarity between the query embedded vector and the stored chunk vector then returns the top k chunks with the highest corresponding similarity score.', metadata={'header_2': '**Text Embedding and Vector Database**'}), embedding=[0.015350341796875, 0.0265045166015625, -0.00962066650390625, -0.0033016204833984375, -0.005558013916015625, -0.01532745361328125, 0.03546142578125, 0.041473388671875, -0.041107177734375, 0.01027679443359375, -2.3424625396728516e-05, 0.01445770263671875, -0.0038280487060546875, -0.010284423828125, -0.006969451904296875, 0.01409149169921875, 0.051361083984375, 0.0147247314453125, -0.020660400390625, 0.0269317626953125, 0.00669097900390625, 0.007274627685546875, -0.00722503662109375, 0.035003662109375, 0.015045166015625, -0.0203094482421875, 0.00295257568359375, 0.009185791015625, 0.0254669189453125, -0.024749755859375, -0.00788116455078125, -0.0230712890625, -0.0267486572265625, -0.0018377304077148438, -0.003086090087890625, 0.0280303955078125, -0.02484130859375, -0.0172576904296875, -0.01032257080078125, 0.049957275390625, 0.01119232177734375, -0.0202484130859375, -0.012176513671875, 0.0262603759765625, -0.03741455078125, 0.025482177734375, 0.00432586669921875, -0.016693115234375, -0.039337158203125, 0.0487060546875, -0.020050048828125, -0.00858306884765625, -0.035980224609375, -0.01032257080078125, 0.007358551025390625, 0.005733489990234375, 0.001239776611328125, 0.0013093948364257812, 0.0276947021484375, -0.0138702392578125, 0.00873565673828125, -0.0379638671875, -0.0188751220703125, 0.0110321044921875, -0.0439453125, -0.01192474365234375, -0.056243896484375, 0.00933074951171875, 0.016754150390625, -0.00783538818359375, 0.0219268798828125, 0.024810791015625, 0.0194091796875, -0.0147247314453125, -0.00417327880859375, -0.00989532470703125, 0.006710052490234375, 0.07794189453125, -0.01360321044921875, -0.05474853515625, 0.004856109619140625, -0.0166168