421875, -0.048370361328125, -0.02166748046875, -0.015716552734375, -0.044525146484375, 0.0215606689453125, 0.0142974853515625, -0.0054931640625, -0.04217529296875, -0.0238494873046875, -0.0005750656127929688, -0.00295257568359375, 0.01776123046875, -0.037353515625]), CompaktEmbeddingEntry(id='45', chunk=CompaktChunk(header=<MarkdownHeader.H2: '##'>, header_type=<MarkdownHeader.H2: '##'>, header_name='3.5 demo ui visualization', content='To facilitate clearer visualization of each phase of the project, we developed a demonstration user interface with use cases aligned to the corresponding stages of the proposed pipeline. This UI main features consist of 4 main use cases:  \\n**==> picture [271 x 409] intentionally omitted <==**  \\n**----- Start of picture text -----**<br>\\nGraphRAG UI<br>Filter & Save to<br>Storage<br>Graph<br><<include>> Representation &<br>Graph Embedding<br><<include>><br>Upload<br>Document<br>Chunked Hierarchy<br>(currently unavailable)<br><<extend>><br>Choose Number<br>of Nodes<br><<include>><br>Explore See Node<br>Graph <<include>> Information<br><<include>><br>User See Graph<br>Structure<br>Vector/ Graph<br>Submit Query <<include>> database retrieval<br><<include>><br>Receive Answer<br><<include>><br>Compare Answer<br>Submit between<br>Feedback Vector/Graph<br>**----- End of picture text -----**<br>  \\n**Figure 17:** UML Use case Diagram  \\n- **Upload Document** : The first use case focuses on document uploading. The system supports the ingestion of documents in `.doc` , `.docx` , and `.pdf` formats and applies a normalization step that converts all inputs into the pdf format for centralized processing. The system then filters the uploaded documents based on predefined criteria for Vietnamese legal document types and disregards files that do not meet these requirements. Documents that satisfy all criteria are stored in an object storage, after which their full textual content is parsed for graph-based representation.  \\nThe system also supports the Chunked Hierarchy technique and Graph embedding for enhancing Graph-integrated context retrieval; however, these features will operate very slowly and are currently only used in experiments.  \\n- **Explore Graph** : After transforming the document into a graph-based representation, the system visualizes the resulting graph as an interactive interface. This interface enables users to inspect the  \\n34  \\nGroup Project  \\nTax Legal Retrieval with Graph Representation Assistant  \\nGroup 55  \\noverall graph structure and navigate to individual nodes to view their associated attributes along with choosing the number of represented nodes.  \\n- **Submit Query** : The user interface supports query execution over both vector databases and graph databases. To limit configuration complexity, the retrieval modes are restricted to similarity-based search for the vector database and hybrid search for the graph database. The system additionally supports parallel retrieval, enabling direct comparison between vector-based and graph-integrated retrieval during answer generation.  \\n- **Feedback Submission** : In addition to receiving generated answers, users are provided with the ability to submit feedback for each individual response through both multiple-choice selections and free-text notes. All feedbacks are stored in a centralized repository to support future system refinement and evaluation.  \\n**==> picture [407 x 472] intentionally omitted <==**  \\n**----- Start of picture text -----**<br>\\nMain UI Document Processor Storage Vectordb Graphdb Query Engine Answer Generator<br>Actor<br>Document Upload<br>Upload<br>document<br>Filter Document<br>Document valid<br>or not<br>Save Document<br>Graph Representation &<br>Node/Graph Embedding<br>Graph Exploration<br>Explore Graph<br>Fetch Graph Nodes<br>Graph Visualization<br>Choose node<br>numbers<br>Limit Node Numbers<br>Revisualize Graph<br>Interact with<br>Node<br>Return Node<br>attributes<br>Query Answers<br>Input Question<br>Process Query<br>Graph Retrieval<br>Vector Retrieval<br>Generate<br>answer<br>Return answers<br>Provide<br>feedback<br>Save<br>feedbacks<br>**----- End of picture text -----**<br>  \\n**Figure 18:** UI Sequence Diagram  \\n35  \\nGroup Project  \\nTax Legal Retrieval with Graph Representation Assistant  \\nGroup 55', metadata={'header_2': '**3.5 Demo UI Visualization**'}), embedding=[-0.04278564453125, 0.0302581787109375, 0.00727081298828125, 0.013763427734375, 0.00910186767578125, -0.00931549072265625, -0.0120391845703125, 0.0168609619140625, -0.0220184326171875, 0.027862548828125, 0.028106689453125, -0.06475830078125, -0.006824493408203125, -0.03057861328125, 0.0224456787109375, -0.001117706298828125, -0.0019989013671875, -0.008209228515625, -0.03387451171875, 0.0256805419921875, 0.05810546875, -0.01552581787109375, 0.03887939453125, 0.006103515625, -0.0164337158203125, -0.03546142578125, 0.0288543701171875, 0.0682373046875, 0.014678955078125, -0.0347900390625, -0.002613067626953125, -0.044891357421875, -0.00984954833984375, -0.0200347900390625, -0.020477294921875, 0.037384033203125, -0.025054931640625, 0.016448974609375, -0.007965087890625, 0.0016164779663085938, 0.0014190673828125, -0.00861358642578125, 0.024383544921875, -0.0068511962890625, -0.00977325439453125, 0.0501708984375, -0.03924560546875, -0.00516510009765625, 0.0003056526184082031, 0.018707275390625, -0.02325439453125, -0.0036144256591796875, -0.018035888671875, -0.01690673828125, 0.0173797607421875, -0.0064544677734375, -0.0297393798828125, -0.0197906494140625, 0.00678253173828125, -0.01395416259765625, 0.027099609375, -0.0184478759765625, 0.0198974609375, 0.049530029296875, -0.0275421142578125, 0.03564453125, -0.0321044921875, -0.0029659271240234375, 0.00876617431640625, -0.0027446746826171875, 0.03924560546875, 0.035797119140625, 0.0212554931640625, -0.009735107421875, 0.05584716796875, 0.0191192626953125, -0.0152740478515625, 0.0023136138916015625, -0.031494140625, -0.04974365234